feat: add requireRole middleware for RBAC enforcement (fl-wmd.1)

Role hierarchy: owner > admin > member > viewer.
- Viewer: read-only access (all GET endpoints)
- Member: resolve/assign/comment/merge/snooze/bulk ops
- Admin: settings, integrations, fingerprint rules, alert rules,
  webhook templates, source maps, teams
- Owner: project registration/removal, API token management

Applied to both API (Bearer auth) and dashboard (session auth) routes.
Auth middleware now sets X-Account-Role header for downstream checks.

